Hash-Search version 0.03
========================

Hash::Search allows a search to be made on a hash based on a regular
expressions pattern based on the name of the key and returns the
results as a seperate hash. It also keeps a count of how many
matches have been made.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

strict
warnings
Carp
Exporter

